data.description: Better than new with all the upgrades included! This home offers solid granite tops in kitchen & baths, stainless steel appliances, spacious kitchen island, custom vent hood & cabinetry. Large family room with a cozy corner gas log fireplace w/split face decorative tile & large windows with lots of natural light. Bedrooms include spacious closets & ceiling fans. Master suite includes a ceiling fan, and a vaulted master ceiling. The master bath includes a walk-in shower, Jetta whirlpool tub, double vanities, and spacious master walk in closet. 2" blinds included throughout! Covered patio comes complete w/wood-burning fireplace, gas outlet for grill and TV hookups. Large fenced backyard. Two car garage with 4-6 person in ground storm shelter installed. Garage door opener. Additional amenities are a complete home air filtration sys, Rinnai tankless heater, outdoor sprinkler system, R44 insulation, & solar boards.
